response.original_title: Jeff Dunham - Election 2024 - Biden vs. Trump How Did We Get Here... Again
response.overview: As most of us know, American politics in the last few years has gotten WAY out of hand… Crazily and sadly. Well, for about a decade now, the little guys and I have done our best to make fun of EVERYONE in charge! SO.. Leave your partisanship at the door, grab your popcorn, and settle in for this not-so-correct compilation of clips from our past political punches! You’ll laugh, you’ll cry, and some of you will be greatly offended… until we make fun of the OTHER side! When it’s all done, let us know YOUR favorite slam!… I mean JOKE!
response.title: Jeff Dunham - Election 2024 - Biden vs. Trump How Did We Get Here... Again
